soccer.common

Interface Data

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByeData, ConnectData, DriveData, EmptyData, HearData, InfoData, InitData, KickData, PeriodData, RefereeData, SeeData, SituationData, TalkData, TeleportData, ViewData

    public interface Data
    This interface defines the operations on the data content in a packet. By implementing this interface, a piece of data can be inserted into a packet and extracted from it
    Author:
    Yu Zhang
